Package: ivgls
Type: Package
Title: Network-Aware IV Regression with Graph-Fused Lasso
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Dhrubajyoti", "Ghosh", email = "dghosh3@kennesaw.edu",
           role = c("aut", "cre"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-3360-3786")),
    person("Samhita", "Pal", email = "samhita.pal@vumc.org",
           role = "aut", comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0001-4930-916X")))
Description: Implements three instrumental variable (IV) estimators for
    causal variable selection when exposures have network structure.
    IV-LASSO applies a standard two-stage LASSO without graph information.
    IVGL incorporates a graph Laplacian penalty in the second stage to
    encourage similar effects among connected nodes. IVGL-S further
    corrects for partially invalid instruments using an alternating
    sisVIVE-style update. Utility functions for graph construction,
    data simulation, and performance evaluation are also provided.
